fraytik ze'mir, m'hot undz tsugebrengt alts mentshn, tsugebrengt undz mentshn nokh.

00:17:19.410 --> 00:17:23.706
nor UNK gekumen eyner a yunger man, take der vos hot bakumen azoy fil shlek,

00:17:23.752 --> 00:17:29.461
gekumen hern mir shrayen, "yidn do zents ets? yidn vu zent ets? yidn vu zent ets?"

00:17:29.569 --> 00:17:33.191
er hot derkent der kol az dos iz eyner fun zayne soldatn,

00:17:33.265 --> 00:17:37.197
vos er iz geven mit im, gevorn a guter fraynt mit im, er iz im gekumen rateven.

00:17:37.547 --> 00:17:41.702
shrayt er aroys, do bin ikh! do bin ikh! Yontshi, ikh veys, do bin ikh!

00:17:41.770 --> 00:17:44.717
o iz er tsugekumen tsu der tir, zogt er, her mikh oys raboysay.

00:17:44.925 --> 00:17:51.771
s'iz di shtot iz shoyn leydik fun daytshn un fun niloshes, dray niloshes zenen geblibn,

00:17:51.152 --> 00:17:53.053
fraytik iz shoyn geven leydik?

00:17:51.827 --> 00:17:55.494
shoyn un leydik, yo s'nokh nisht geven, ober azoy iz gevezn, azoy hot er gezogt.

00:17:55.494 --> 00:18:03.043
ets zent geblibn, dray niloshes zenen geblibn, un dray niloshes zenen gekumen enk shisn, enk oystsushisn, nokh dem geyen zey vayter.

00:18:04.230 --> 00:18:06.637
